Package: fdrregGenomics
Type: Package
Title: Genomics-Integrated False Discovery Rate Regression Pipeline
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Jinghong", "Qiu",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "1155132472@link.cuhk.edu.hk")
Description: A comprehensive pipeline for integrating GWAS summary statistics
    with biological annotations using False Discovery Rate Regression (FDRreg).
    Supports SNP-level, MAGMA gene-level, and TWAS (S-PrediXcan / S-MultiXcan)
    analyses with optional sample-overlap decorrelation and variable selection.
    The underlying FDRreg algorithm is developed by Scott et al. (2016, JASA).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    FDRreg,
    powerplus,
    glmnet,
    HelpersMG,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
